And know that I care.

00:32:14.082 --> 00:32:23.024 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Focus on the joys in life,
Not the burdens that we bear.

00:32:23.024 --> 00:32:29.063 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Think about what God has done.
To show his love, he gave his Son.

00:32:29.063 --> 00:32:36.838 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
