00:34:42.697 --> 00:34:51.973 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
One day at a time—
One day at a time.

00:34:58.880 --> 00:35:02.416 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We’re not alone, for he is there.

00:35:02.416 --> 00:35:06.020 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We have his words of comfort and true friends

00:35:06.020 --> 00:35:08.022 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
who really care.”

00:35:08.022 --> 00:35:11.125 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What an encouraging thought from that song!

00:35:11.125 --> 00:35:16.063 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yes, true friends who share
our love for Jehovah are invaluable.

00:35:17.165 --> 00:35:20.034 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’ll see that in this story from Japan.

00:35:20.034 --> 00:35:24.172 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Sisters Takako Sato and Hisako Wakui

00:35:24.172 --> 00:35:28.342 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
have worked together as pioneers since 1957.

00:35:28.342 --> 00:35:30.711 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Let’s learn how their friendship

00:35:30.711 --> 00:35:33.548 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
has helped them serve Jehovah with joy.

00:35:34.549 --> 00:35:36.617 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We are pioneer partners.

00:35:38.452 --> 00:35:40.521 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’ve been working together

00:35:40.521 --> 00:35:43.024 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for over 60 years.

00:35:43.024 --> 00:35:45.660 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In 1956,

00:35:45.660 --> 00:35:49.897 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I was the only Jehovah’s Witness
in Nagano prefecture.

00:35:49.897 --> 00:35:52.099 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It was lonesome,

00:35:52.099 --> 00:35:55.369 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but I applied for regular pioneer service.

00:35:55.369 --> 00:35:57.605 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Surprisingly,

00:35:57.605 --> 00:36:01.142 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I was appointed
as a special pioneer.

00:36:01.142 --> 00:36:04.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I was so happy that I found myself

00:36:04.812 --> 00:36:07.815 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
rolling around on the tatami-mat floor

00:36:07.815 --> 00:36:10.751 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with the appointment letter in my hand.

00:36:10.751 --> 00:36:13.821 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That was the way
I expressed my joy and appreciation.

00:36:15.156 --> 00:36:17.225 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When I was invited to serve

00:36:17.225 --> 00:36:19.760 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
as a special pioneer,
I was sent to Nagano,

00:36:19.760 --> 00:36:23.030 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and that’s where I met Hisako.

00:36:23.030 --> 00:36:26.801 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Takako and I focused on our ministry.

00:36:28.436 --> 00:36:31.672 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When an isolated group was established,

00:36:31.672 --> 00:36:33.841 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
since there were no brothers,

00:36:33.841 --> 00:36:36.744 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I would wear a head covering
and conduct the meetings.

00:36:38.246 --> 00:36:41.282 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Sometimes the outlines were in English.

00:36:41.282 --> 00:36:43.050 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We didn’t understand anything.

00:36:44.919 --> 00:36:47.321 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But people were delighted to hear

00:36:47.321 --> 00:36:51.726 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
even just the scriptures and went home satisfied,

00:36:51.726 --> 00:36:55.730 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and that strongly impressed on me
the power of God’s Word.

00:36:58.599 --> 00:37:03.404 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We were assigned
to a territory in the city after that.

00:37:03.404 --> 00:37:06.774 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We found so many not-at-homes,

00:37:06.774 --> 00:37:11.112 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but we were determined to meet people.

00:37:11.112 --> 00:37:13.281 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So we changed the times we preached,

00:37:13.281 --> 00:37:15.483 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and we talked to people on the street

00:37:15.483 --> 00:37:17.285 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
who were going to work.

00:37:17.285 --> 00:37:20.721 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We cherished even small opportunities.

00:37:20.721 --> 00:37:23.925 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When we had a chance to meet a householder,

00:37:23.925 --> 00:37:26.994 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we always tried to have a conversation

00:37:26.994 --> 00:37:29.563 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that we could link to the next visit.

00:37:29.563 --> 00:37:34.001 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Before long, I had ten Bible studies.

00:37:35.603 --> 00:37:38.406 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Takako acts like she’s cheerful,

00:37:38.406 --> 00:37:43.144 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but she’s been fighting various illnesses.

00:37:43.144 --> 00:37:46.914 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
At times, it was so bad

00:37:46.914 --> 00:37:50.117 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that I could not even go out in service.

00:37:50.117 --> 00:37:53.754 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I had a serious skin condition.

00:37:53.754 --> 00:37:56.157 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I could not bear

00:37:56.157 --> 00:38:00.061 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to look at the illustration of Job in the magazine,

00:38:00.061 --> 00:38:02.797 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and I covered it up with paper.

00:38:06.767 --> 00:38:09.437 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But Jehovah helped me
to look to Job’s example.

00:38:10.871 --> 00:38:12.440 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I learned

00:38:12.440 --> 00:38:14.909 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that our endurance under trial

00:38:14.909 --> 00:38:17.712 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
would become praise to God.

00:38:19.380 --> 00:38:22.249 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I have often had health problems.

00:38:23.851 --> 00:38:26.220 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Just at one of those times,

00:38:26.220 --> 00:38:29.023 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I received a letter from the branch.

00:38:29.023 --> 00:38:31.359 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It said:

00:38:31.359 --> 00:38:34.762 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“What you
can accomplish now may be limited.

00:38:36.163 --> 00:38:40.101 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“However, think
about all that you have done up to now

00:38:40.101 --> 00:38:42.236 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“to give praise to Jehovah

00:38:42.236 --> 00:38:46.974 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“and about the people
you were able to help learn the truth,

00:38:46.974 --> 00:38:51.712 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and be joyful knowing
that you have been used by Jehovah fully.”

00:38:54.548 --> 00:38:56.584 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I couldn’t stop crying

00:38:56.584 --> 00:39:00.221 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
because I really felt the care and concern

00:39:00.221 --> 00:39:03.157 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
from the organization and from Jehovah.

00:39:05.726 --> 00:39:09.196 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Hisako also
took really good care of me

00:39:09.196 --> 00:39:11.198 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and prayed with me.

00:39:13.200 --> 00:39:16.470 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our thinking and personalities are different,

00:39:16.470 --> 00:39:20.441 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but we made efforts to talk things out.

00:39:20.441 --> 00:39:25.379 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our heartfelt desire
to want to serve Jehovah full-time

00:39:25.379 --> 00:39:28.682 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
has always been the same.

00:39:30.117 --> 00:39:33.187 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
For 60 years, we’ve enjoyed

00:39:33.187 --> 00:39:36.724 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a truly wonderful life of service to Jehovah.

00:39:36.724 --> 00:39:40.728 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah has supported us in difficult times

00:39:40.728 --> 00:39:44.098 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
through the Bible, the organization, and friends.

00:39:44.098 --> 00:39:47.802 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I have tasted the truthfulness of the words:

00:39:47.802 --> 00:39:52.440 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“When I am weak, then I am powerful.”

00:39:54.608 --> 00:39:58.312 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‘When I said: “My foot is slipping,”

00:39:58.312 --> 00:40:02.183 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
your kindness, O Jehovah, has supported me.’

00:40:02.183 --> 00:40:05.753 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I can say that too.

00:40:05.753 --> 00:40:09.090 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Although we don’t have energy or ability,

00:40:09.090 --> 00:40:13.461 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we’ve been able to enjoy
full-time service together up until now.

00:40:15.296 --> 00:40:17.231 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’m really content now.

00:40:17.231 --> 00:40:20.234 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s all thanks to Jehovah.

00:40:23.370 --> 00:40:27.608 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Like the apostle Paul,
our sisters cultivated singleness

00:40:27.608 --> 00:40:31.011 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and focused on full-time service to Jehovah

00:40:31.011 --> 00:40:33.447 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for more than 60 years.

00:40:33.447 --> 00:40:36.350 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yes, they face everyday challenges

00:40:36.350 --> 00:40:39.120 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and the extra ones that come with age,

00:40:39.120 --> 00:40:43.357 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but their heartfelt desire
to serve Jehovah whole-souled

00:40:43.357 --> 00:40:48.195 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
brings Takako and Hisako
real joy and contentment.

00:40:48.996 --> 00:40:53.601 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Whole-souled service
for nearly 20,000 brothers and sisters

00:40:53.601 --> 00:40:57.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is a full-time assignment at Bethel.

00:40:57.104 --> 00:41:01.675 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What motivates them
to reach out for this special privilege?

00:41:01.675 --> 00:41:04.345 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What blessings do they experience?

00:41:04.345 --> 00:41:09.183 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And what’s the best way
to prepare and qualify for Bethel service?

00:41:09.183 --> 00:41:12.253 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’d like to invite my friend Patrick LaFranca

00:41:12.253 --> 00:41:14.588 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to discuss these and other questions.

00:41:14.588 --> 00:41:15.990 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Welcome, Pat.

00:41:15.990 --> 00:41:17.658 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Thank you, Ron.

00:41:18.826 --> 00:41:20.327 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How heartwarming it’s been

00:41:20.327 --> 00:41:23.964 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to see millions take their stand for true worship!

00:41:23.964 --> 00:41:27.535 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Thousands more are joining us every week.

00:41:27.535 --> 00:41:30.971 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah is speeding up the ingathering work,

00:41:30.971 --> 00:41:33.908 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and this makes us very happy.

00:41:33.908 --> 00:41:38.579 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But who will work
to provide the Bibles, Bible literature,

00:41:38.579 --> 00:41:41.015 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and the audio and video publications

00:41:41.015 --> 00:41:43.083 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that sustain us spiritually

00:41:43.083 --> 00:41:47.721 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and help us to accomplish
our Kingdom preaching and teaching work?

00:41:47.721 --> 00:41:50.858 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Bethel is a unique place.

00:41:50.858 --> 00:41:53.227 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s where mature Christians

00:41:53.227 --> 00:41:55.629 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
render sacred service to Jehovah

00:41:55.629 --> 00:41:58.999 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in close association with Christ’s brothers.

00:41:58.999 --> 00:42:02.870 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They minister to the needs
of our worldwide brotherhood

00:42:02.870 --> 00:42:05.673 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and support the preaching work.

00:42:05.673 --> 00:42:09.643 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Bethel family is a group of dedicated,

00:42:09.643 --> 00:42:11.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
baptized servants of Jehovah

00:42:11.812 --> 00:42:14.782 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
who live and work together closely.

00:42:14.782 --> 00:42:18.285 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So they experience in a special way

00:42:18.285 --> 00:42:21.555 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
what Psalm 133:1 says:

00:42:21.555 --> 00:42:24.325 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Look! How good

00:42:24.325 --> 00:42:27.027 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“and how pleasant it is for brothers

00:42:27.027 --> 00:42:29.430 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to dwell together in unity!”

00:42:29.430 --> 00:42:33.500 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’re very pleased to see
that many have expanded their service

00:42:33.500 --> 00:42:36.971 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to Jehovah by making themselves available

00:42:36.971 --> 00:42:40.274 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for the special privilege of Bethel service.

00:42:40.274 --> 00:42:43.143 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Have you considered this as a goal?

00:42:44.612 --> 00:42:46.614 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Making yourself available

00:42:46.614 --> 00:42:50.017 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for Bethel service
is like knocking on a door that leads

00:42:50.017 --> 00:42:52.920 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to many other privileges of service.

00:42:52.920 --> 00:42:55.422 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Of course, to serve at Bethel requires

00:42:55.422 --> 00:42:57.658 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a self-sacrificing spirit

00:42:57.658 --> 00:42:59.493 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and a willingness to serve

00:42:59.493 --> 00:43:03.264 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
wherever there is a need,
in harmony with the attitude displayed

00:43:03.264 --> 00:43:06.433 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
by the prophet Isaiah at Isaiah 6:8:

00:43:06.433 --> 00:43:10.337 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Then I heard the voice of Jehovah saying:

00:43:10.337 --> 00:43:13.907 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“‘Whom shall I send, and who will go for us?’

00:43:13.907 --> 00:43:18.912 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And I said: ‘Here I am! Send me!’”

00:43:18.912 --> 00:43:21.715 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When Isaiah learned about an opportunity

00:43:21.715 --> 00:43:23.717 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to do more in Jehovah’s service,

00:43:23.717 --> 00:43:25.719 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
he responded eagerly,

00:43:25.719 --> 00:43:27.888 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
even though he did not know exactly

00:43:27.888 --> 00:43:30.357 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
what he was going to be assigned to do.

00:43:30.357 --> 00:43:32.426 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It was enough for him to know that Jehovah

00:43:32.426 --> 00:43:36.363 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
was extending an invitation
to serve in a special way,

00:43:36.363 --> 00:43:39.433 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and Isaiah wanted to volunteer.

00:43:39.433 --> 00:43:43.103 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The same spirit is shown
by Bethel family members worldwide.

00:43:45.439 --> 00:43:48.175 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What especially motivates
so many to serve at Bethel?

00:43:49.443 --> 00:43:51.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Love for Jehovah moves us

00:43:51.812 --> 00:43:54.815 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to put Kingdom interests ahead of self-interest.

00:43:54.815 --> 00:43:58.652 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As stated in the Proclaimers book, page 295:

00:43:58.652 --> 00:44:01.322 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“This is not work in which they gain

00:44:01.322 --> 00:44:04.325 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“personal prominence or material possessions.

00:44:04.325 --> 00:44:07.828 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Their desire is to honor Jehovah,
and they are satisfied

00:44:07.828 --> 00:44:10.064 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“with the provisions made for them

00:44:10.064 --> 00:44:11.965 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“in the way of food, lodging,

00:44:11.965 --> 00:44:14.735 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and a modest [allowance]
for personal expenses.”

00:44:16.036 --> 00:44:19.506 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Are there any rewards
that come from serving in this unique way?

00:44:20.574 --> 00:44:23.043 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Those who have offered themselves willingly

00:44:23.043 --> 00:44:26.013 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for Bethel service have truly been blessed.

00:44:27.748 --> 00:44:31.719 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
The love and unity we feel here is incomparable.

00:44:31.719 --> 00:44:34.154 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s not like in a company out in the world

00:44:34.154 --> 00:44:37.825 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
because here you can work
with your friends every day.

00:44:39.426 --> 00:44:41.195 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
Like-minded people

00:44:41.195 --> 00:44:43.530 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
have the same goals and support each other.

00:44:43.530 --> 00:44:44.732 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That is what you can feel here.

00:44:46.033 --> 00:44:47.735 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
Maybe you’re assigned a task

00:44:47.735 --> 00:44:50.104 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
that you’ve never performed before,

00:44:50.104 --> 00:44:52.473 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but there are
many experienced brothers and sisters

00:44:52.473 --> 00:44:55.342 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
who can help
—professionally as well as personally.

00:44:56.677 --> 00:45:00.781 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
Whether it is the consideration of the daily text

00:45:00.781 --> 00:45:02.783 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or the Watchtower Study with the Bethel family,

00:45:02.783 --> 00:45:05.052 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
listening to the practical, valuable comments

00:45:05.052 --> 00:45:08.522 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of our brothers and sisters is really refreshing.

00:45:08.522 --> 00:45:10.357 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You really feel that they love Jehovah,

00:45:10.357 --> 00:45:12.926 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and their comments help you to feel the same.

00:45:14.395 --> 00:45:16.463 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
Here in Bethel, you have the best Employer

00:45:16.463 --> 00:45:18.465 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
that there is—Jehovah.

00:45:18.465 --> 00:45:22.236 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
No other employer
is as grateful and considerate as he is,

00:45:22.236 --> 00:45:25.239 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
so out of love for Jehovah,
you’re simply happy to give him your best.

00:45:26.940 --> 00:45:28.442 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
Whenever I think about what

00:45:28.442 --> 00:45:30.077 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
is being done at Bethel

00:45:30.077 --> 00:45:31.445 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
—publications are being

00:45:31.445 --> 00:45:32.579 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
produced and shipped,

00:45:32.579 --> 00:45:35.182 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
videos for our conventions are being made,

00:45:35.182 --> 00:45:37.451 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and translation is being done

00:45:37.451 --> 00:45:39.720 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
into so many different languages—

00:45:39.720 --> 00:45:41.255 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I keep getting goose bumps.

00:45:42.256 --> 00:45:44.258 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
No matter what I can do here,

00:45:44.258 --> 00:45:46.393 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
knowing that by doing it

00:45:46.393 --> 00:45:49.630 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I am supporting Christ’s brothers
makes me feel very, very good.

00:45:51.131 --> 00:45:53.133 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So how does a young person

00:45:53.133 --> 00:45:55.869 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
qualify for Bethel service?

00:45:55.869 --> 00:45:59.139 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
My parents raised me to have

00:45:59.139 --> 00:46:00.774 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a spiritual focus.

00:46:00.774 --> 00:46:02.776 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So during the school holidays

00:46:02.776 --> 00:46:06.747 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and growing up,
our life revolved around the ministry

00:46:06.747 --> 00:46:08.749 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—doing spiritual activities.

00:46:08.749 --> 00:46:09.950 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And it really helped us

00:46:09.950 --> 00:46:13.987 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
keep focused spiritually as a family

00:46:13.987 --> 00:46:17.658 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and helped me stay focused
on the goals that I wanted to achieve.

00:46:17.658 --> 00:46:20.594 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I really enjoy reading,

00:46:20.594 --> 00:46:22.329 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and one day my Dad just said to me,

00:46:22.329 --> 00:46:24.865 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Why don’t you read the Bible?”

00:46:24.865 --> 00:46:27.167 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And I know it sounds obvious,
but at that point, I had never read it

00:46:27.167 --> 00:46:29.636 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
from Genesis to Revelation.

00:46:29.636 --> 00:46:31.638 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So when I finished reading the Bible,

00:46:31.638 --> 00:46:35.242 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
it really changed my thinking,

00:46:35.242 --> 00:46:39.213 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and it really proved the truth to myself.

00:46:39.213 --> 00:46:43.317 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And this helped me to keep

00:46:43.317 --> 00:46:47.855 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a spiritual focus, and it really was the first step

00:46:47.855 --> 00:46:49.857 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in reaching out and achieving

00:46:49.857 --> 00:46:52.025 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the spiritual goals that I wanted to achieve.

00:46:52.025 --> 00:46:54.962 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In the congregation, I was able to help out

00:46:54.962 --> 00:46:57.631 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with doing the magazines
and the sound and the platform.

00:46:59.032 --> 00:47:02.803 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And these privileges really helped me to build

00:47:02.803 --> 00:47:05.806 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a good work ethic and give in ways

00:47:05.806 --> 00:47:07.808 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that I could give more to Jehovah.

00:47:07.808 --> 00:47:10.811 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So the elders used to work
with me a lot in the ministry.

00:47:10.811 --> 00:47:12.980 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So when I felt

00:47:12.980 --> 00:47:14.982 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that ‘I can’t do this’

00:47:14.982 --> 00:47:16.984 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or ‘This is too much’ or ‘It’s too overwhelming’

00:47:16.984 --> 00:47:21.054 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or ‘I’ll never be able to reach this goal,’
an elder showed me

00:47:21.054 --> 00:47:23.957 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a scripture in the Bible where Jehovah

00:47:23.957 --> 00:47:26.894 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
was encouraging Joshua to be courageous.

00:47:26.894 --> 00:47:29.897 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And that really impacted me,

00:47:29.897 --> 00:47:34.902 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
so that I was able to be courageous,
too, and to reach my goal of Bethel.

00:47:36.503 --> 00:47:38.505 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So when I visited Bethel,

00:47:38.505 --> 00:47:41.441 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I saw that they were normal people,

00:47:41.441 --> 00:47:44.878 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and they had so many good qualities

00:47:44.878 --> 00:47:47.114 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that I wanted to imitate

00:47:47.114 --> 00:47:49.182 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—very hospitable, very warm,

00:47:49.182 --> 00:47:52.286 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
very inviting.

00:47:52.286 --> 00:47:56.456 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That helped me to want to reach my goal,
so that I could be like them.

00:47:57.391 --> 00:47:59.226 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To serve at Bethel

00:47:59.226 --> 00:48:01.428 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
there are qualifications that need to be met.

00:48:01.428 --> 00:48:04.965 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You should have a deep love for Jehovah

00:48:04.965 --> 00:48:07.668 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and the organization, which is demonstrated

00:48:07.668 --> 00:48:10.437 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
by living in harmony with Bible standards.

00:48:10.437 --> 00:48:12.906 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You must have a fine reputation

00:48:12.906 --> 00:48:14.908 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
as a spiritual person.

00:48:14.908 --> 00:48:16.944 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You should have respect

00:48:16.944 --> 00:48:18.946 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for Jehovah’s moral standards,

00:48:18.946 --> 00:48:21.982 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
avoiding uncleanness and sexual immorality.

00:48:21.982 --> 00:48:24.051 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You should have a clean conscience

00:48:24.051 --> 00:48:27.020 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
before Jehovah and be at peace with yourself

00:48:27.020 --> 00:48:29.222 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and with Jehovah’s organization.

00:48:30.090 --> 00:48:32.993 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Your dress and grooming should be exemplary,

00:48:32.993 --> 00:48:35.095 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
befitting a Christian minister

00:48:35.095 --> 00:48:37.230 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
even during leisure time.

00:48:37.230 --> 00:48:39.232 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Styles that are faddish

00:48:39.232 --> 00:48:41.935 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or extreme or that identify us

00:48:41.935 --> 00:48:44.438 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with undesirable elements of the world

00:48:44.438 --> 00:48:46.707 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
are not acceptable at Bethel.

00:48:47.908 --> 00:48:50.611 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The applicant should not read, listen to,

00:48:50.611 --> 00:48:53.013 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or view any type of material

00:48:53.013 --> 00:48:55.282 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that is inappropriate for a Christian.

00:48:55.282 --> 00:48:57.417 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Such unwholesome material

00:48:57.417 --> 00:48:59.720 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
certainly would include pornography,

00:48:59.720 --> 00:49:03.323 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
debasing music, or any kind of entertainment

00:49:03.323 --> 00:49:05.659 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that features sexual immorality,

00:49:05.659 --> 00:49:08.295 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
spiritism, or violence.

00:49:09.162 --> 00:49:11.164 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Bethel applicants should be

00:49:11.164 --> 00:49:14.067 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
from 19 to 35 years of age.

00:49:14.067 --> 00:49:16.303 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Occasionally, there is an opening

00:49:16.303 --> 00:49:18.572 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for someone over 35 years of age

00:49:18.572 --> 00:49:20.574 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
who may have specialized skills

00:49:20.574 --> 00:49:22.576 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that are needed at Bethel,

00:49:22.576 --> 00:49:24.578 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
such as those with certain technical

00:49:24.578 --> 00:49:27.814 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or medical experience, translation skills,

00:49:27.814 --> 00:49:31.818 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or building trades such as plumbing, electrical,

00:49:31.818 --> 00:49:35.288 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
heavy equipment mechanics, or carpentry.

00:49:35.288 --> 00:49:37.924 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Those with such capabilities and training

00:49:37.924 --> 00:49:39.926 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
are welcome to apply.

00:49:40.994 --> 00:49:43.063 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In view of the unique demands

00:49:43.063 --> 00:49:45.198 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of a full-time assignment at Bethel,

00:49:45.198 --> 00:49:48.669 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
you should be mentally and emotionally sound,

00:49:48.669 --> 00:49:52.172 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
physically strong, and able to work long hours.

00:49:53.140 --> 00:49:54.975 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You should be able to read, write,

00:49:54.975 --> 00:49:56.977 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and speak the primary language

00:49:56.977 --> 00:49:58.979 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of the branch territory.

00:49:58.979 --> 00:50:01.148 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This will enable you to communicate well

00:50:01.148 --> 00:50:03.150 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with others serving at Bethel,

00:50:03.150 --> 00:50:06.186 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to receive needed training, and to work safely

00:50:06.186 --> 00:50:08.355 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in the Bethel environment.

00:50:09.056 --> 00:50:11.058 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Bethel applicants agree to serve

00:50:11.058 --> 00:50:13.060 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for a minimum of one year,

00:50:13.060 --> 00:50:15.462 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
during which time you will receive training

00:50:15.462 --> 00:50:17.631 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for continued Bethel service.

00:50:19.032 --> 00:50:22.536 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With regard to secular skills,
we do not encourage individuals

00:50:22.536 --> 00:50:25.539 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to obtain university education

00:50:25.539 --> 00:50:28.108 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or training with the thought that this will improve

00:50:28.108 --> 00:50:30.711 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
their chances of being called into Bethel.

00:50:30.711 --> 00:50:33.814 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The best way to prepare for Bethel service

00:50:33.814 --> 00:50:37.517 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is to first serve in the full-time pioneer ministry.

00:50:38.752 --> 00:50:41.555 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The greatest need is for single brothers.

00:50:41.555 --> 00:50:44.958 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
However, all who meet
the qualifications, including sisters,

00:50:44.958 --> 00:50:49.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
are encouraged to apply
for temporary volunteer service.

00:50:49.229 --> 00:50:52.132 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Serving as
a temporary volunteer at Bethel may open

00:50:52.132 --> 00:50:54.134 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the way to other opportunities

00:50:54.134 --> 00:50:57.404 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to expand your service to Jehovah.

00:50:57.404 --> 00:51:00.273 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If you are interested
in applying for Bethel service,

00:51:00.273 --> 00:51:03.376 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
which application should you request

00:51:03.376 --> 00:51:05.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
from a member
of your Congregation Service Committee?

00:51:05.812 --> 00:51:07.814 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Since there are two types

00:51:07.814 --> 00:51:10.751 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of applications available, first give careful

00:51:10.751 --> 00:51:12.753 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and prayerful consideration

00:51:12.753 --> 00:51:14.755 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to your circumstances.

00:51:14.755 --> 00:51:18.825 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Thereafter, decide whether
you will request from the elders

00:51:18.825 --> 00:51:21.061 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the Application for Volunteer Program (A-19),

00:51:21.061 --> 00:51:23.830 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
which is available for those interested

00:51:23.830 --> 00:51:25.999 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in serving on a temporary basis

00:51:25.999 --> 00:51:28.235 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for as brief as one week or as long

00:51:28.235 --> 00:51:30.370 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
as several consecutive months.

00:51:30.370 --> 00:51:32.739 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Or you may decide to request

00:51:32.739 --> 00:51:35.675 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the Application to Become
a Member of the Worldwide Order

00:51:35.675 --> 00:51:40.046 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of Special Full-Time Servants
of Jehovah’s Witnesses (A-8).

00:51:40.046 --> 00:51:42.816 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This application is for those interested

00:51:42.816 --> 00:51:44.985 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in serving on a long-term basis

00:51:44.985 --> 00:51:47.454 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for one full year or longer.

00:51:47.454 --> 00:51:50.590 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If the Branch Committee
determines that there is a need

00:51:50.590 --> 00:51:52.659 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for your services, they will decide

00:51:52.659 --> 00:51:55.695 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
where you can best be used, whether at Bethel

00:51:55.695 --> 00:51:58.365 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or perhaps on
a theocratic construction assignment.

00:51:59.966 --> 00:52:02.469 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Submitting your application may open

00:52:02.469 --> 00:52:04.504 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a door of opportunity to serve Jehovah

00:52:04.504 --> 00:52:07.641 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and his organization in a variety of ways.

00:52:10.443 --> 00:52:12.946 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Of course, not all of us

00:52:12.946 --> 00:52:16.283 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
who have such a self-sacrificing spirit

00:52:16.283 --> 00:52:20.153 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
have the circumstances in life to serve at Bethel.

00:52:20.153 --> 00:52:23.423 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But we can encourage others who do.

00:52:23.423 --> 00:52:26.359 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Parents, follow the example

00:52:26.359 --> 00:52:28.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of God-fearing parents

00:52:28.562 --> 00:52:31.264 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
such as Hannah and Elkanah,

00:52:31.264 --> 00:52:33.900 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
who willingly made their son available

00:52:33.900 --> 00:52:37.003 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for expanded theocratic privileges.

00:52:37.003 --> 00:52:41.708 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Continue to place the goal
of Bethel service before your young ones,

00:52:41.708 --> 00:52:45.212 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and stimulate
their interest in the full-time ministry

00:52:45.212 --> 00:52:49.583 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
by your example and your positive expressions.

00:52:49.583 --> 00:52:51.585 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If possible,

00:52:51.585 --> 00:52:55.989 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
bring them on tour
of world headquarters in New York, U.S.A.,

00:52:55.989 --> 00:53:00.093 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or make arrangements
to bring them on a tour of the Bethel

00:53:00.093 --> 00:53:03.563 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in the branch territory in which you live.

00:53:03.563 --> 00:53:07.701 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Such visits can help
young ones to witness firsthand

00:53:07.701 --> 00:53:12.372 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the work that’s being done
at Bethel to promote Kingdom interests.

00:53:12.372 --> 00:53:16.443 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Elders, help young ones in your congregation

00:53:16.443 --> 00:53:18.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
who have the potential to expand their service

00:53:18.812 --> 00:53:22.482 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to Jehovah to meet the qualifications.

00:53:22.482 --> 00:53:26.586 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah continues to look
for those willing to respond

00:53:26.586 --> 00:53:30.857 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to his invitation to expand their service to him.

00:53:30.857 --> 00:53:33.627 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As in Isaiah’s day, He asks:

00:53:33.627 --> 00:53:37.530 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Whom shall I send, and who will go for us?”

00:53:37.530 --> 00:53:40.667 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Will you answer as did the prophet:

00:53:40.667 --> 00:53:43.470 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Here I am! Send me!”

00:53:43.470 --> 00:53:47.274 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We encourage you to progress to spiritual maturity

00:53:47.274 --> 00:53:49.676 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and serve Jehovah whole-souled.

00:53:49.676 --> 00:53:53.446 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In due time, you may qualify to serve at Bethel

00:53:53.446 --> 00:53:57.284 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or in another form of exciting theocratic service

00:53:57.284 --> 00:54:00.086 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that permits you to use the health and strength

00:54:00.086 --> 00:54:03.590 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that Jehovah has granted you in an expanded way,

00:54:03.590 --> 00:54:05.625 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
all to his praise.

00:54:07.093 --> 00:54:09.963 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Please be assured that we love you

00:54:09.963 --> 00:54:12.065 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for the willing spirit you show

00:54:12.065 --> 00:54:15.902 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
as you continue to reach out in Jehovah’s service.

00:54:17.137 --> 00:54:19.172 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Thank you, Pat.

00:54:19.172 --> 00:54:22.909 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We hope
that the information Brother LaFranca shared

00:54:22.909 --> 00:54:25.011 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
motivates many more to have

00:54:25.011 --> 00:54:29.282 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the prophet Isaiah’s willing and self-sacrificing spirit.

00:54:29.282 --> 00:54:33.053 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So much of what Jehovah provides encourages us

00:54:33.053 --> 00:54:35.755 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to keep busy with spiritual things.

00:54:35.755 --> 00:54:39.926 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
For one,
we’re looking forward to our upcoming conventions.

00:54:39.926 --> 00:54:44.331 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The theme for this year is “‘Love Never Fails’!”

00:54:44.331 --> 00:54:47.100 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Would you like a preview of the program?

00:54:47.100 --> 00:54:49.102 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Let’s take a look.

00:54:49.102 --> 00:54:51.705 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Love

00:54:51.705 --> 00:54:53.306 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—is it gone?

00:54:55.976 --> 00:54:58.445 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Have we lost it?

00:54:59.846 --> 00:55:01.681 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Is it the possession of the wealthy?

00:55:03.249 --> 00:55:05.518 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the strong?

00:55:06.319 --> 00:55:08.555 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Or is it somewhere else?

00:55:09.656 --> 00:55:13.626 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
At the 2019 convention of Jehovah’s Witnesses,

00:55:13.626 --> 00:55:16.629 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
you will learn what real love is,

00:55:16.629 --> 00:55:18.331 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
where to find it,

00:55:18.331 --> 00:55:19.966 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and how to show it

00:55:19.966 --> 00:55:22.535 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and have it shown in return.

00:55:27.207 --> 00:55:30.310 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
God cares deeply about you.

00:55:30.310 --> 00:55:31.444 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And he wants you to know

00:55:31.444 --> 00:55:33.813 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that in this hate-filled world,

00:55:33.813 --> 00:55:37.350 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
love can be found.

00:55:37.350 --> 00:55:39.786 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It is not lost.

00:55:39.786 --> 00:55:44.290 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And that love will never fail.

00:55:49.229 --> 00:55:53.400 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As we’ve discussed,
we should never underestimate the power

00:55:53.400 --> 00:55:57.804 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of our brotherhood
to help us overcome worries and anxiety.

00:55:57.804 --> 00:56:02.242 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our conventions are wonderful opportunities
for us to encourage one another

00:56:02.242 --> 00:56:06.846 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
by the hundreds,
thousands, and tens of thousands.

00:56:06.846 --> 00:56:09.916 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And this year, we’re especially excited

00:56:09.916 --> 00:56:12.819 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that 24 international conventions

00:56:12.819 --> 00:56:15.121 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
will be held throughout the world.

00:56:15.121 --> 00:56:20.126 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Use the opportunity
to get to know more of your brothers and sisters

00:56:20.126 --> 00:56:25.031 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
at the regional
or international convention you attend.

00:56:25.031 --> 00:56:27.567 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To conclude this month’s program,

00:56:27.567 --> 00:56:30.303 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
let’s visit our brothers in Turkey.

00:56:30.303 --> 00:56:34.674 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Turkey is a nation of more than 80 million people

00:56:34.674 --> 00:56:38.044 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and a land rich in Bible history.

00:56:39.245 --> 00:56:44.250 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Turkey occupies a unique geographic position,
bridging Europe and Asia.

00:56:45.552 --> 00:56:49.255 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s here that Noah’s ark
came to rest near Mount Ararat,

00:56:49.255 --> 00:56:51.691 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Turkey’s highest mountain.

00:56:52.759 --> 00:56:56.262 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This is the land
of the congregations in Colossae and Galatia,

00:56:56.262 --> 00:56:58.598 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
as well as all seven congregations

00:56:58.598 --> 00:57:00.633 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
mentioned in Revelation.

00:57:01.901 --> 00:57:04.070 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The territory is diverse and vast,

00:57:04.070 --> 00:57:07.040 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with a publisher-to-population ratio

00:57:07.040 --> 00:57:10.310 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of 1 to more than 26,000.

00:57:12.011 --> 00:57:14.047 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In the capital city of Ankara,

00:57:14.047 --> 00:57:16.349 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a single congregation is working hard

00:57:16.349 --> 00:57:19.853 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to reach almost 5.5 million people.

00:57:21.654 --> 00:57:26.659 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Many congregations in Turkey
focus on public witnessing, with encouraging results.

00:57:27.727 --> 00:57:30.263 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Let’s visit the Hatay Congregation,

00:57:30.263 --> 00:57:33.700 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
near the ancient city of Syrian Antioch.

00:57:33.700 --> 00:57:38.538 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Paul used Antioch
as his home base for his missionary tours.

00:57:38.538 --> 00:57:43.543 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And it was here
that the disciples were first called Christians.

00:57:43.543 --> 00:57:45.078 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Today,

00:57:45.078 --> 00:57:48.481 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
this part of Turkey is known for its food

00:57:49.782 --> 00:57:53.820 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—such as spices, herbs, fruits, and sweets.

00:57:53.820 --> 00:57:55.822 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In recent times,

00:57:55.822 --> 00:57:59.626 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
unrest and war have disrupted the region.

00:57:59.626 --> 00:58:04.097 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Some of our brothers and sisters
have been so near to the conflict

00:58:04.097 --> 00:58:08.868 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that they could hear
explosions from bombs and gunfire.

00:58:08.868 --> 00:58:12.238 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Despite these threats and anxieties,

00:58:12.238 --> 00:58:17.177 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the 56 publishers, including 11 regular pioneers

00:58:17.177 --> 00:58:20.146 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and 2 special pioneers, attend the meetings

00:58:20.146 --> 00:58:23.082 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and preach without letup.

00:58:23.082 --> 00:58:27.520 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our brothers and sisters
in Turkey send their love and greetings

00:58:27.520 --> 00:58:29.722 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to the worldwide brotherhood.

00:58:29.722 --> 00:58:34.627 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our love goes back to them
for their zeal and steadfast faith.

00:58:34.627 --> 00:58:37.830 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
From the World Headquarters
of Jehovah’s Witnesses,

00:58:37.830 --> 00:58:40.500 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
this is JW Broadcasting.

